<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">寺考</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">二、本寺建築物沿革</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">四　後山之禪室</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">水池區</cb:mulu>
